OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,For thunderstorms easing and skies
OL,7,Fclearing to leave a fine, dry night.
OL,8,FRather warm for many eastern areas,
OL,9,Falthough feeling slightly fresher in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSome sunshine likely, although
OL,13,Fprobably largely cloudy through the
OL,14,Fmiddle of the day with a risk of
OL,15,Fshowers, perhaps thundery. Slightly
OL,16,Fcooler for many areas, but still
OL,17,Fgenerally very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
