OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,6,Flargely sunny and very warm, locally
OL,7,Fhot on Saturday. Trending cooler and
OL,8,Fmore changeable from Sunday. An
OL,9,Fincreased chance of rain, but still
OL,10,Fsome fine, warm weather at times.
